    "created_at": "2016-02-29T19:10:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-02-29T19:10:54Z",
    "body": "I think the problem is that the asar.unpacked dir isn't included in the list of nodejs-searchable dirs (used by require statements). Maybe there is some way to configure this, but I found that editing the path works just as well. Kind of a pain, but it works.\n\n`__dirname.replace('app.asar', 'app.asar.unpacked') + '/path/to/thing';`\n"
  },
